I have run successfully multiple times R CMD install, build and check in my local Ubuntu 20.04, and cannot reproduce the error. Does anyone have any idea what I could possibly do to troubleshoot the error? I have seen the TIMEOUT occur in at least two consecutive build reports, so I do not think it is something spurious.

Thanks a lot in advance!

Best wishes,

Lara


